be changed by direct manipulation of the window. Other important features 
of its appearance are controlled through two options in the  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
Options #!EF pull-down menu in the Image window menu bar:  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   
View Control #!EF and  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   AutoAxes #!EF . #!N #!N #!N 
